 y pr\u00e1cticas que han llevado a la costumbre de utilizarlo en nuestros d\u00edas como adorno navide\u00f1o, s\u00edmbolo de dicha y protecci\u00f3n.", "language": null, "image": "https://s0.wp.com/i/blank.jpg", "pagetype": "website", "links": ["#content", "https://xeniuspharma.wordpress.com/", "https://xeniuspharma.wordpress.com/", "https://xeniuspharma.wordpress.com/contacto/", "https://xeniuspharma.wordpress.com/para-medicos/", "https://xeniuspharma.wordpress.com/productos/", "https://xeniuspharma.wordpress.com/productos/helixor-a-m-y-p/", "https://xeniuspharma.wordpress.com/productos/helleborus/", "https://xeniuspharma.wordpress.com/quienes-somos/", "https://xeniuspharma.wordpress.com/proposito/", "https://xeniuspharma.wordpress.com/", "https://xeniuspharma.wordpress.com/2015/09/13/que-es-la-medicina-antroposofica/", "https://xeniuspharma.wordpress.com/2015/09/13/que-es-la-medicina-antroposofica/", "https://xeniuspharma.wordpress.com/author/valeryxenius/", "https://xeniuspharma.wordpress.com/category/medicina-antroposofica/", "https://xeniuspharma.wordpress.com/2015/09/13/que-es-la-medicina-antroposofica/#respond", "https://xeniuspharma.wordpress.com/2015/08/15/bendita-planta/", "https://xeniuspharma.wordpress.com/2015/08/15/bendita-planta/", "https://xeniuspharma.wordpress.com/author/valeryxenius/", "https://xeniuspharma.wordpress.com/category/medicina-antroposofica/", "https://xeniuspharma.wordpress.com/2015/08/15/bendita-planta/#respond", "https://xeniuspharma.wordpress.com/2015/08/15/bendita-planta/#more-118", "https://xeniuspharma.wordpress.com/2015/08/15/muerdago-contra-el-cancer/", "https://xeniuspharma.wordpress.com/2015/08/15/muerdago-contra-el-cancer/", "https://xeniuspharma.wordpress.com/author/valeryxenius/", "https://xeniuspharma.wordpress.com/category/medicina-antroposofica/", "https://xeniuspharma.wordpress.com/2015/08/15/muerdago-contra-el-cancer/#respond", "https://quimiotips.files.wordpress.com/2014/08/packung_tanne_spritze.jpg", "https://xe